        public Company​(java.lang.String name,
               java.lang.String add1,

        Initializes the field locations instance variable to contain the location information passed into the constructor. A BillTo location is created and added to the list of locations for a company constructed with the name passed into the parameter. An empty string is passed to the name of the billing contact parameter. Sets the name of the business to parameter name.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the company
        add1 - street address
        city - the city
        state - the state
        zip - the zip code
        country - the country
